<bibRefCitation author="Nuss M. &amp; Landry B. &amp; Vegliante F. &amp; Trankner A. &amp; Mally R. &amp; Hayden J. E. &amp; Bauer F. &amp; Segerer A. &amp; Li H. &amp; Schouten R. &amp; Solis M. A. &amp; Trofimova T. &amp; De Prins J. &amp; Speidel W." journalOrPublisher="Last accessed" pageId="22" pageNumber="337" pagination="2003 - 2016" part="1" refString="Nuss M., Landry B., Vegliante F., Trankner A., Mally R., Hayden J. E., Bauer F., Segerer A., Li H., Schouten R., Solis M. A., Trofimova T., De Prins J., Speidel W. 2003 - 2016. Global Information System on Pyraloidea. www. pyraloidea. org. Last accessed: 1 June 2016." title="Global Information System on Pyraloidea. www. pyraloidea. org" type="journal article" year="2016">
